{"id": "firmware-development--fw-radiomaster-bandit-nano-wip", "title": "FW Radiomaster Bandit Nano WIP", "forum": "firmware-development", "messages": [{"id": "1464713431809659002", "author": "gjelsoe", "author_handle": "cossie1413", "user_id": "297128333332709377", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/297128333332709377/d677b018cc6072f37763a51d37bb76f1.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Saturday, January 24, 2026 3:08 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-24 3:08 p.m.", "text": "Hi there, I've been working on getting Radiomaster Bandit Nano/Micro working with MeshCore. Also working on Radiomaster Bandit basic support. Current work can be accessed at my github here : https://github.com/gjelsoe/MeshCore", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Hi there, I&#39;ve been working on getting Radiomaster Bandit Nano/Micro working with MeshCore.\n\nAlso working on Radiomaster Bandit basic support.\n\nCurrent work can be accessed at my github here :\n<a href=\"https://github.com/gjelsoe/MeshCore\">https://github.com/gjelsoe/MeshCore</a></span></div>", "embeds_html": ["<div class=chatlog__embed><div class=chatlog__embed-color-pill style=background-color:rgba(30,35,39,255)></div><div class=chatlog__embed-content-container><div class=chatlog__embed-content><div class=chatlog__embed-text><div class=chatlog__embed-title><a class=chatlog__embed-title-link href=https://github.com/gjelsoe/MeshCore><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">GitHub - gjelsoe/MeshCore: A new lightweight, hybrid routing mesh p...</div></a></div><div class=chatlog__embed-description><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">A new lightweight, hybrid routing mesh protocol for packet radios - gjelsoe/MeshCore</div></div></div><div class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-container><a class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-link href=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/oC2J_xLkDFZZjXByha6FrQ1ImyuK3g2eym1z1CTLRQI/https/opengraph.githubassets.com/c3223963d6a2674a00f3adadd027a006a1ab043e46865a51452d5aad5aeab537/gjelsoe/MeshCore> <img class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail src=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/oC2J_xLkDFZZjXByha6FrQ1ImyuK3g2eym1z1CTLRQI/https/opengraph.githubassets.com/c3223963d6a2674a00f3adadd027a006a1ab043e46865a51452d5aad5aeab537/gjelsoe/MeshCore alt=Thumbnail loading=lazy data-canonical-url=https://opengraph.githubassets.com/c3223963d6a2674a00f3adadd027a006a1ab043e46865a51452d5aad5aeab537/gjelsoe/MeshCore> </a></div></div></div></div>"], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1465079136656687206", "author": "gjelsoe", "author_handle": "cossie1413", "user_id": "297128333332709377", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/297128333332709377/d677b018cc6072f37763a51d37bb76f1.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Sunday, January 25, 2026 3:21 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-25 3:21 p.m.", "text": "Radiomaster Bandit Nano and Micro are ready for more testing, the larger Bandit (CNC Model) should also be usable but still needs work.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Radiomaster Bandit Nano and Micro are ready for more testing, the larger Bandit (CNC Model) should also be usable but still needs work.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1465770433063289075", "author": "gjelsoe", "author_handle": "cossie1413", "user_id": "297128333332709377", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/297128333332709377/d677b018cc6072f37763a51d37bb76f1.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Tuesday, January 27, 2026 1:08 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-27 1:08 p.m.", "text": "Radiomaster Bandit now supports TX and New message LED with configurable color. It still have 2 buttons available for other stuff. The Bandit and Bandit Nano Five-way joystick could be very handy for Canned messages.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Radiomaster Bandit now supports TX and New message LED with configurable color.\nIt still have 2 buttons available for other stuff.\n\nThe Bandit and Bandit Nano Five-way joystick could be very handy for Canned messages.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1468349909571997992", "author": "gjelsoe", "author_handle": "cossie1413", "user_id": "297128333332709377", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/297128333332709377/d677b018cc6072f37763a51d37bb76f1.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Tuesday, February 3, 2026 3:58 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-02-03 3:58 p.m.", "text": "Submitted as PR to MC", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Submitted as PR to MC</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1469024541086060768", "author": "robb", "author_handle": "azrobb", "user_id": "281604556746391554", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/281604556746391554/50ea22a22ce6baebd8646959b1ed49ca.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Thursday, February 5, 2026 12:39 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-02-05 12:39 p.m.", "text": "Thanks for this! BLE companion builds/works well on the larger Bandit but I needed to add +<helpers/ui/AnalogJoystick.cpp> to the repeater section in platformio.ini to build without errors (undefined references to AnalogJoystick).", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Thanks for this! BLE companion builds/works well on the larger Bandit but I needed to add +&lt;helpers/ui/AnalogJoystick.cpp&gt; to the repeater section in platformio.ini to build without errors (undefined references to AnalogJoystick).</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1469045758933336147", "author": "gjelsoe", "author_handle": "cossie1413", "user_id": "297128333332709377", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/297128333332709377/d677b018cc6072f37763a51d37bb76f1.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Thursday, February 5, 2026 2:03 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-02-05 2:03 p.m.", "text": "Ups, missed that one. Moved it to [radiomaster_900_bandit] / [radiomaster_900_bandit_nano] section. Updated github with the lines moved.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Ups, missed that one. Moved it to [radiomaster_900_bandit] / [radiomaster_900_bandit_nano] section.\n\nUpdated github with the lines moved.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=thumbsup><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=👍 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f44d.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1472188912163356846", "author": "gjelsoe", "author_handle": "cossie1413", "user_id": "297128333332709377", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/297128333332709377/d677b018cc6072f37763a51d37bb76f1.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Saturday, February 14, 2026 6:13 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-02-14 6:13 a.m.", "text": "Also playing with Canned Messages for it (edited)", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Also playing with Canned Messages for it</span> <span class=chatlog__edited-timestamp title=\"Saturday, February 14, 2026 6:23 a.m.\">(edited)</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1472191546148257843"